Data formats
============


train/*.trn:
------------
{entity_id}-{review_index} {review_rating}
<one sentence per line, split into EDUs>
...
------------


gold/aspects/*[dev/tst].asp:
----------------------------
<aspect titles separated by '|'>

{entity_id}-{review_index}
<edu1> [tab] <aspect indices>
<edu2> [tab] <aspect indices>
...
----------------------------


gold/polarities/*.pol:
----------------------
{entity_id}-{review_index}-{edu_index} [tab] polarity
...
----------------------


gold/polarities/discrete/*.lbl:
-------------------------------
{review_rating} {entity_id}-{review_index}
{label} [tab] <edu text>
...
-------------------------------


gold/polarities/salience/*.sal:
-------------------------------
{entity_id}-{review_index}-{edu_index} [tab] [ann1] [ann2] [ann3]
...
-------------------------------


gold/summaries/*/[all/pos/neg]/*:
---------------------------------
<one extracted edu per line>
...
---------------------------------
